				</h1>
				<div class="roles">
					<span class="role">üë©‚Äçüíª Developer <span class="invert">üë©‚Äçüíª Developer</span></span>&nbsp;
					<span class="role">‚ù§Ô∏è Tech Mentor <span class="invert">‚ù§Ô∏è Tech Mentor</span></span>&nbsp;
